       Rampage growls, and also sees the cliff edge. It could be now, or 
never. Rampage uses all his remaining strenght, and pushes Demise closer and 
closer, all the while the injuries in his back leave a trail in the snow. 
"Shall we go together?" He says, because with Demises claws dug into his 
back, thier is no escape. So, with a final push, both bots tumble down the 
cliff headed towrd the river of ice.

       Paralysis has no time to notice the water before he is knocked several 
times from above. The left side of his face is no longer present, and his 
innards are exposed.
       Inferno rams into Scather, and sinks his fangs into the bot, chowing 
down and holding him tight at the same time.
       Paralysis, or what once was him, drew his pistol in the air and fired, 
meanwile the mech drizzled down his chest, legs, and on to the snow. Now it 
appeared if the battle was taking place on a giant dalmation.

       Tankkor was enraged beyond anything describable. Endgame was a 
difficult opponent. Tankkor was now going to use a large sum of energy, but 
it would be worth it.
       Suddenly, Tannkors optic laser, missles, plasma discharges, and turret 
bullets unleased in a spectical of light. All headed at Endgame.

--part1_9b.e50c575.276e7f22_boundary
